259
0:13:55.782,000 --> 0:13:58,000
when one draws cartoons and when one hallucinates them.

260
0:13:59.036,000 --> 0:14:02,000
It's very interesting that that should be specific.

261
0:14:02.316,000 --> 0:14:05,000
